ategory:The Corporate Ministry members]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Marietta, Georgia]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestlers from Georgia (U.S. state)]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling managers and valets]]\n[[Category:The New World Order (professional wrestling) members]]\n[[Category:WWE Hall of Fame inductees]]\n", "name_user": "Fylindfotberserk", "label": "safe", "comment": "Generalformattingbyscript", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Big_Boss_Man_(wrestler)"}
