n_sq_mi       = \n|area_metro_km2         = \n|area_metro_sq_mi       = \n|population_as_of       = 2003\n|population_footnotes   = \n|population_note        = \n|population_total       = 38,833\n|population_density_km2 = \n|population_density_sq_mi = \n|population_metro       =\n|population_density_metro_km2 =\n|population_density_metro_sq_mi =\n|population_urban       = \n|population_density_urban_km2 =\n|population_density_urban_mi2 =\n|timezone = Indochina Time\n|utc_offset = +07:00\n|latd=|latm=|lats=|latNS=|longd=|longm=|longs=|longEW=}}\n\n'''Na R\u00ec''' is a [[huy\u1ec7n|rural district]] of [[B\u1eafc K\u1ea1n Province]] in the [[Northeast (Vietnam)|Northeast]] region of Vietnam. As of 2003 the district had a population of 38,833.<ref name=\"Statoids\">{{cite web|url=http://www.statoids.com/yvn.html|title=Districts of Vietnam|publisher=Statoids|accessdate=13 March 2009}}</ref> The district covers an area of 834&nbsp;km\u00b2. The district capital lies at [[Y\u1ebfn L\u1ea1c]].<ref name=\"Statoids\"/>\n\n==Administrative divisions==\nThe district is divided into one township: [[Y\u1ebfn L\u1ea1c]] (the district capital) and communes:\n\n#[[\u0110\u1ed5ng X\u00e1]]\n#[[Li\u00eam Th\u1ee7y]]\n#[[Xu\u00e2n D\u01b0\u01a1ng, B\u1eafc K\u1ea1n|Xu\u00e2n D\u01b0\u01a1ng]]\n#[[D\u01b0\u01a1ng S\u01a1n]]\n#[[Quang Phong, B\u1eafc K\u1ea1n|Quang Phong]]\n#[[H\u1ea3o Ngh\u0129a]]\n#[[C\u01b0 L\u1ec5]]\n#[[H\u1eefu Th\u00e1c]]\n#[[C\u00f4n Minh]]\n#[[V\u0103n Minh]]\n#[[\u00c2n T\u00ecnh]]\n#[[Lam S\u01a1n, B\u1eafc K\u1ea1n|Lam S\u01a1n]]\n#[[Kim L\u01b0]]\n#[[L\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u00e0nh]]\n#[[L\u1ea1ng San]]\n#[[Kim H\u1ef7]]\n#[[L\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng]]\n#[[V\u0103n H\u1ecdc]]\n#[[L\u01b0\u01a1ng H\u1ea1]]\n#[[C\u01b0\u1eddng L\u1ee3i, B\u1eafc K\u1ea1n|C\u01b0\u1eddng L\u1ee3i]]\n#[[V\u0169 Loan]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n{{coord|22.167|N|106.083|E|type:adm2nd_region:VN|display=title}}\n\n{{Districts of Northeast Vietnam}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Na Ri District}}\n[[Category:Districts of B\u1eafc K\u1ea1n Province]]\n{{BacKan-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Redirect|Na Ri|Miss Korea 2008|Na Ree}}\n{{distinguish|Nari (disambiguation){{!}}Nari}}\n{{Expand Vietnamese|Na R\u00ec|date=March 2009}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n|name                   = Na R\u00ec District\n|settlement_type        = [[Huy\u1ec7n|District]]\n|official_name          = \n|other_name             = \n|native_name            = Huy\u1ec7n Na R\u00ec\n|nickname               = \n|motto                  = \n|image_skyline          = \n|imagesize              = \n|image_caption          = \n|image_flag             = \n|flag_size              = \n|image_seal             = \n|seal_size              = \n|image_shield           = \n|shield_size            =\n|image_blank_emblem     =\n|blank_emblem_size      =\n|image_map              = \n|mapsize                = \n|map_caption            = \n|image_map1             = \n|mapsize1               = \n|map_caption1           =\n|pushpin_map            = \n|pushpin_label_position = \n|subdivision_type       = Country\n|subdivision_name       = {{flag|Vietnam}}\n|subdivision_type1      = [[Provinces of Vietnam|Province]]\n|subdivision_name1      = [[B\u1eafc K\u1ea1n Province|B\u1eafc K\u1ea1n]]\n|subdivision_type2      = \n|subdivision_name2      = \n|seat_type              = Capital\n|seat                   = [[Y\u1ebfn L\u1ea1c]]\n|government_type        =\n|leader_title           = \n|leader_name            = \n|leader_title1          =  <!-- for places with, say, both a mayor and a city manager -->\n|leader_name1           =\n|established_title      =  \n|established_date       = \n|area_magnitude         = \n|unit_pref              = Imperial<!--Enter: Imperial, if Imperial (metric) is desired-->\n|area_footnotes         = \n|area_total_km2         =  \n|area_land_km2          = 834\n|area_water_km2         = \n|area_total_sq_mi       = \n|area_land_sq_mi        = \n|area_water_sq_mi       = \n|area_water_perce